name: 2018 UoA Karate Gasshuku
description: Two days jammed full of training. 4th Dan Dave Sensei from Wellington will be attending as a guest instructor.
extendedDescription: Two days jammed full of training. 4th Dan Dave Sensei from Wellington will be attending as a guest instructor. Our usual instructors will also be teaching but expect to see a range of different topics covered. Saturday: 11.30 - 6pm. Sunday 10am - 5pm. Lunch will be catered both days and there will be group dinners both nights.

name: 40th IOGKF Sekai Budosai
